Nostrand Avenue, east side, between Myrtle and Vernon Avenues, showing the farm buildings on the Boerum farm. Before modern streets were laid out the farm was reached by way of Cripple Bush Road.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  about 1900

Nostrand Ave., east side, between Myrtle and Vernon Aves. This view is taken, looking southeast. The house at the left, faces on Vernon Ave. The orchard is all that remains of the Boerum farm.

About 1910.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
